{"id":160109,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/06/译者-《译者》每日原文推荐-2011610/","date":"2011-06-11T10:30:26Z","modified":"2011-06-11T18:02:33Z","title":"译者 | 《译者》每日原文推荐  2011/6/10","content":"<p><p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以下为每日原文推荐。如果你有兴趣，请参与翻译并将译文寄给</span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://yyyyiiii.blogspot.com/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《译者》</span></a><b>(</b><span><b><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"mailto:iyizhe@gmail.com\"><span>iyizhe@gmail.com</span></a>)</span></b></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以便与大家共享。欢迎使用</span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feedburner.google.com/fb/a/mailverify?uri=yizhe&#038;loc=en_US\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">邮件组</span></a><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">、</span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://goo.gl/f1NDK\">Google Reader</a><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">和推特（</span><span><span>@yigroup</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">）跟踪我们的最新消息。</span></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【热点时评】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美联社</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://news.yahoo.com/s/ap/20110610/ap_on_re_as/as_china_dissident_release\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">四川地震维权人士黄琦被释放出狱</span></a> </span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——尚不清楚他是否会在家中被软禁</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《卫报》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2011/jun/10/zeng-jinyan-hu-jia-blogger-evicted\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国人权活动家被赶出家门</span></a> </span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——警方逼房东赶走胡佳妻子曾金燕</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">西藏风情网</span><span> &#8211; <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.tibetcustom.com/article.php/20110608184225583#.TfEwHMZtY60;gmail\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">联合国专家小组对西藏僧侣“被失踪”表示关切</span></a> </span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——按照国际法，“被失踪”属于违法行为。</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《经济学人》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.economist.com/blogs/prospero/2011/06/chinese-censorship&#038;fsrc=nwl\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">草泥马，河蟹</span></a> </span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——洪天健的“脑残游记”展在曼哈顿展出</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《外交事务》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.foreignaffairs.com/articles/67734/kanan-makiya/what-is-totalitarian-art?page=show\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">什么是专制主义艺术？</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——很红很暴力</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国辩论</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.chinadebate.com/2011/06/looking-down-from-tiananmen/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">从天安门城头往下看</span></a> </span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——安迪沃霍尔笔下的毛主席像，很黄很梦露</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《基督教科学箴言报》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.csmonitor.com/Commentary/Global-Viewpoint/2011/0608/Francis-Fukuyama-Democracy-still-rules.-But-will-US-catch-up-in-a-changing-world\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">民主仍然是主流，但是美国能追上世界的新变化吗？</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——福山访谈录</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span>CNN – <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.cnn.com/2011/WORLD/asiapcf/06/10/china.military.superpower/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国什么时候变成超级大国？</span></a> </span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——皇帝不急太监急</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《外交事务》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.foreignaffairs.com/articles/67477/thomas-j-christensen/the-advantages-of-an-assertive-china\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">自信的中国有好处</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——在核扩散和气候问题上，美国需要更为自信的中国作为伙伴</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《外交事务》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.foreignaffairs.com/articles/67479/charles-glaser/will-chinas-rise-lead-to-war\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国的崛起会导致战争吗？</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——作者的观点是“不会”</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约时报》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2011/06/11/world/asia/11vietnam.html?partner=rssnyt&#038;emc=rss\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">南海冲突升级</span></a> </span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——越南表示抗议，要搞实弹演习</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">赫芬顿邮报</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.huffingtonpost.com/jeff-danziger/chinese-aircraft-carrier_b_874109.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国的航母【政治漫画】</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“沃尔玛号”</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《航空周刊》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.aviationweek.com/aw/generic/story_channel.jsp?channel=defense&#038;id=news/awst/2011/06/06/AW_06_06_2011_p56-327956.xml\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">印度空军司令以中国为心腹之患</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——他认为印度的空中优势在逐渐被缩小</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《外交政策》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.foreignpolicy.com/articles/2011/06/08/pyongyang_spring\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">平壤之春？</span></a> </span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——别做梦了</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">法新社</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.google.com/hostednews/afp/article/ALeqM5iG1c2e0wdMSRuVrNeSzXrazE0ltw?docId=CNG.2d0364df4f09fe91f0929404deff47c1.611\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国金融评级机构称美国已经无力偿债</span></a> </span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——赶紧把美国买下来吧！</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">布鲁金斯研究所</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.brookings.edu/papers/2011/0610_shanghai_financial_center_elliott.aspx?rssid=china&#038;utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+BrookingsRSS%2Ftopics%2Fchina+%28Brookings%3A+Topics+-+China%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">在上海建立全球金融中心</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——来自其他金融中心城市的观点（</span><span>18</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">页</span><span>PDF</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">文件）</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《商业周刊》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.businessweek.com/news/2011-06-10/china-reports-less-than-estimated-13-billion-trade-surplus.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国公布五月贸易盈余达</span>130<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">亿美元</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——低于预期数量</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《外交事务》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.foreignaffairs.com/articles/67810/joseph-gagnon-and-gary-hufbauer/taxing-chinas-assets\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">对中国所持的美国国债收税？！</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——既可以增加美国就业率，又不用打贸易战</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华尔街日报》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://blogs.wsj.com/chinarealtime/2011/06/09/chinese-tech-ceos-pledge-to-walk-red-road/?mod=WSJBlog\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国的</span>GDP<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">数据有谱没有？</span></a> </span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——李克强说数据是“人造”的。你说呢？</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《经济学人》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>–<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.economist.com/node/18805673?fsrc=rss\"> <span lang=\"ZH-CN\">红色警报</span></a> </span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中国在美上市公司的账目问题疑团重重</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约时报》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" name=\"OLE_LINK4\"></a><a rel=\"nofollow\" name=\"OLE_LINK3\"><span></span></a><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2011/06/10/world/asia/10china.html?_r=1&#038;partner=rss&#038;emc=rss\"><span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">浑水公司成为某些中国企业的眼中钉</span></span></span><span><span></span></span></a></span><span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——浑水公司揭露中国上市企业的浑水摸鱼行为</span></span></span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《商业周刊》</span><span> &#8211; <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.businessweek.com/news/2011-06-09/china-s-sina-extends-losses-after-biggest-fall-since-2008.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">新浪继续亏损，股票现</span>2008<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">年以来最大跌幅</span></a></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华尔街日报》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424052702304778304576375810359779964.html?mod=WSJ_hp_LEFTWhatsNewsCollection\">Facebook<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">在中国面临考验：言论自由值几钱？</span></a> </span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——不得不想起出卖灵魂的浮士德</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【社会百态】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《经济学人》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.economist.com/node/18806177?story_id=18806177&#038;fsrc=rss\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">扼住三峡的喉咙</span></a> </span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——大雨虽然缓解了旱情，可是并没有减少三峡的争议</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《福布斯》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://blogs.forbes.com/rebeccafannin/2011/06/09/china-the-new-assertiveness/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国的新自信</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——</span><span>40</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">岁以下的中国精英在发起第二波创业潮</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《卫报》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/2011/jun/09/china-hollywood-film-industry\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">好莱坞能侍候得了中国十亿电影观众吗？</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中国将成为世界第二大电影市场。观众更爱好莱坞呢，还是国产片呢？</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/5425822223623422432-4501808872328783287?l=yyyyiiii.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=738338\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"738338\"><